snippet.title: The Windows Are Gone - Trailer
snippet.description:
Haunted by grief and guilt after a tragic accident, you start seeing a house in your dreams. No matter what you do, you can't get its image out of your mind. You feel it calling for you, so you answer it.

The Windows Are Gone is releasing on Steam and itch.io on October 2nd

Wishlist now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2590250/The_Windows_Are_Gone/
